{"type": "article", "id": 17781, "title": "补丁贴", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-19T06:30:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 68, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134829Pe2YgS5bspToMxDi.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个补丁贴，原本是口袋一样大小的长方形薄片，浸泡在热水之后就改变了原本的固体形状，成为一个强力修补工具。可以理解成一块彩色的橡皮泥，冷却后又僵硬了。它能剪裁成任何形状去修补，或者用它进行塑形，做成手机架之类的东西。英国设计师 Peter Marigold 开发了这款产品，使用淀粉基生物塑胶材料，<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/formcard/formcard-melt-mould-make-mend\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134827V1g7XJaxPIfRscr6.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"457\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55867971\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021348271ZH8C2tvzj3J6Kmk.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1227\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021348286Qd310ZPrDgKs9lY.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1227\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134828XmpshrSzLYW6dFEj.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"457\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55867971\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134829yCQVHMWo3A5js6xT.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"462\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56479218\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n"}